# CPM100-25 Cycloidal Joint Module

![CPM100-25](images/cpm100-25.jpg)

## Overview

CPM100-25 is a compact cycloidal robotic joint module designed for humanoid robots, quadruped robots and industrial automation systems.

The module integrates:

- Cycloidal Reducer
- High Torque BLDC Motor
- Precision Bearings
- Encoder Interface
- Driver Integration Option

## Specifications

| Parameter | Value |
|------------|------------|
| Outer Diameter | 100 mm |
| Thickness | 29.5 mm |
| Rated Torque | 25 Nm |
| Peak Torque | 75 Nm |
| Rated Speed | 60 rpm |
| Voltage | 24-48V |
| Backlash | 0.05° |

## Applications

- Humanoid Robot Hip Joint
- Humanoid Robot Knee Joint
- Robot Arm Shoulder Joint
- Exoskeleton Systems

## Features

- Low Backlash
- High Torque Density
- Compact Structure
- Lightweight Design
- Robot Ready

## OEM & ODM

Custom mechanical interfaces and communication protocols are available.
# SG6010C Planetary Joint Module

## Overview

SG6010C is a compact planetary robotic joint module with integrated motor and controller.

Designed for:

- Humanoid Robots
- Exoskeleton Systems
- Service Robots
- Lightweight Robot Arms

## Specifications

| Parameter | Value |
|------------|------------|
| Diameter | 80 mm |
| Thickness | 34.07 mm |
| Reduction Ratio | 9.67 |
| Rated Torque | 6 Nm |
| Peak Torque | 18 Nm |
| Rated Speed | 310 rpm |
| Motor Power | 328 W |
| Voltage | 24-48V |
| Weight | 377 g |
| Backlash | 15-20 arcmin |

## Communication

- CAN Bus
- MIT Protocol
- USB Configuration

## Features

- Integrated Drive Electronics
- Compact Design
- High Torque Density
- Robot Ready
